import React from 'react';

import {
  Container,
  ContentContainer,
  TitleContainer,
  SubTitle,
  ImageContainer,
  ThumbnailProject,
  ThumbnailLink,
  ThumbnailImage,
  ThumbnailTitle,
  ThumbnailDescription,
} from './styles';

import imageIIDS from 'src/assets/projects/iids.jpg';

const Project: React.FC = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <ContentContainer>
        <TitleContainer>Projects</TitleContainer>
        <SubTitle>
          Aqui estão alguns dos meus trabalhos, foram realizados em torno de 182
          projetos. Separei alguns dos projetos próprios ou realizados em
          parceria nessa sessão
        </SubTitle>
        <ImageContainer>
          <ThumbnailProject>
            <ThumbnailLink>
              <ThumbnailImage src={imageIIDS} />
              <ThumbnailTitle>Titulo</ThumbnailTitle>
              <ThumbnailDescription>Descrição</ThumbnailDescription>
            </ThumbnailLink>
          </ThumbnailProject>
          <ThumbnailProject>
            <ThumbnailLink>
              <ThumbnailImage src={imageIIDS} />
              <ThumbnailTitle>Titulo</ThumbnailTitle>
              <ThumbnailDescription>Descrição</ThumbnailDescription>
            </ThumbnailLink>
          </ThumbnailProject>
          <ThumbnailProject>
            <ThumbnailLink>
              <ThumbnailImage src={imageIIDS} />
              <ThumbnailTitle>Titulo</ThumbnailTitle>
              <ThumbnailDescription>Descrição</ThumbnailDescription>
            </ThumbnailLink>
          </ThumbnailProject>
          <ThumbnailProject>
            <ThumbnailLink>
              <ThumbnailImage src={imageIIDS} />
              <ThumbnailTitle>Titulo</ThumbnailTitle>
              <ThumbnailDescription>Descrição</ThumbnailDescription>
            </ThumbnailLink>
          </ThumbnailProject>
          <ThumbnailProject>
            <ThumbnailLink>
              <ThumbnailImage src={imageIIDS} />
              <ThumbnailTitle>Titulo</ThumbnailTitle>
              <ThumbnailDescription>Descrição</ThumbnailDescription>
            </ThumbnailLink>
          </ThumbnailProject>
          <ThumbnailProject>
            <ThumbnailLink>
              <ThumbnailImage src={imageIIDS} />
              <ThumbnailTitle>Titulo</ThumbnailTitle>
              <ThumbnailDescription>Descrição</ThumbnailDescription>
            </ThumbnailLink>
          </ThumbnailProject>
        </ImageContainer>
      </ContentContainer>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Project;
